Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:05.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:07.02,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,It's spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:09.03,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,I've graduated high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:10.88,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,and I start my job today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:31.06,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm going to be working...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:32.98,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,...at a game company!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:37.48,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm Suzukaze Aoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:39.11,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:40.55,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm Suzukaze Aoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.55,0:00:42.31,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:46.31,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,Today's the day I become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.31,0:00:47.52,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:53.44,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,Wait, can I really go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:55.52,Main,rin,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:00:57.54,Main,rin,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:01:01.49,Main,rin,0,0,0,,This is a company, so no kids allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.94,0:01:04.29,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:07.46,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Wait, I'm not a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.98,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'll be working at Eagle Jump starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:12.62,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I am Suzukaze Aoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.62,0:01:14.53,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:17.70,Main,rin,0,0,0,,Oh, you were a new employee?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:19.47,Main,rin,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.69,0:01:22.00,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm sorry as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:23.58,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,My name is Suzukaze Aoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:25.52,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Have you heard about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.09,0:01:27.76,Main,rin,0,0,0,,Suzukaze...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:29.48,Main,rin,0,0,0,,Oh, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:31.12,Main,rin,0,0,0,,We're on the same team.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:34.67,Main,rin,0,0,0,,I'm Toyama Rin. I'm an AD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:35.61,Main,rin,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:37.94,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm speaking with a real professional!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:48.00,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,So... You must be busy being an AD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:49.71,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I see it quite often on the TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:51.64,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,but there are so many intricate tasks,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:53.45,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,and they look so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:58.41,Main,rin,0,0,0,,Oh, my AD doesn't stand \Nfor "assistant director."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:01:59.94,Main,rin,0,0,0,,I'm an art director.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:05.35,Main,rin,0,0,0,,So my job is to manage all the artwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:11.36,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:12.06,Main,rin,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:14.19,Main,rin,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:54.81,Main,rin,0,0,0,,This is your desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:58.69,Main,rin,0,0,0,,Oh, would you like something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:00.80,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Oh, may I have orange—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:03.59,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,No, I'm an adult now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.92,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Coffee. Black please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:11.01,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm so glad she seems nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.40,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a professional \Nstarting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:17.61,Main,ko,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:21.28,Main,ko,0,0,0,,No more...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.03,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Is it a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:32.33,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.87,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,P-P-P-P-P-P-Panties...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:56.85,Main,ko,0,0,0,,A middle schooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.24,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Why is a kid here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:04:59.79,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm not a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:01.22,Main,rin,0,0,0,,Oh, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:03.09,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Rin, who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:04.42,Main,rin,0,0,0,,She's our new employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:06.00,Main,rin,0,0,0,,Suzukaze Aoba-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.99,Main,rin,0,0,0,,Oh, this is mine, but do you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.65,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:10.49,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:12.45,Main,ko,0,0,0,,So where is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.87,Main,ko,0,0,0,,This isn't sweet at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:18.62,Main,rin,0,0,0,,Oops, then that's hers. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:19.54,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.15,Main,ko,0,0,0,,You have a mature taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:22.42,Main,ko,0,0,0,,You drink coffee black?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:23.90,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.72,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,This is no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:31.06,Main,ko,0,0,0,,You can't drink it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:34.27,Main,ko,0,0,0,,So how old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.37,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm eighteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:37.52,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Wow, you're a high school grad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:38.79,Main,ko,0,0,0,,That's rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.07,Main,ko,0,0,0,,But you don't even look like a high schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.42,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.61,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.11,Main,ko,0,0,0,,How old do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:49.86,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:52.07,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,I can't just say whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:53.86,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:56.21,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,A poster of {\i1}Fairies Story{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:58.19,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Oh, you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:00.69,Main,ko,0,0,0,,That's the first game I was involved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:01.29,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:04.00,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I was totally into it in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:06.76,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,That's how I found out about this company...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:11.31,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,D-D-Don't tell me... you're thir—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:12.94,Main,ko,0,0,0,,I'm not that old!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:14.21,Main,ko,0,0,0,,I'm twenty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:16.49,Main,ko,0,0,0,,I joined after high school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:19.95,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:21.90,Main,rin,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.40,Main,rin,0,0,0,,By the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:26.52,Main,rin,0,0,0,,How old do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:27.84,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Twenty-three?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:29.61,Main,ko,0,0,0,,We're the same age!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:30.41,Main,rin,0,0,0,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.97,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I-It's such an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:37.83,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm meeting with the people who \Nmade the game I loved as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:40.96,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I especially loved the character design.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:42.60,Main,rin,0,0,0,,My.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:46.92,Main,rin,0,0,0,,She's Yagami Ko who did the \Ncharacter designs for {\i1}Fairies Story{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:50.46,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,You're {\i1}the{\i0} Yagami-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:52.05,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Well that earned me respect easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:55.93,Main,rin,0,0,0,,She will be your manager starting today,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.75,Main,rin,0,0,0,,so I hope you two get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.58,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I-I'll do my betht!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:03.75,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Hey, you bit your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.72,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,P-Please forget that happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:10.14,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,I quickly finished my introduction \Nto my team members
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:11.20,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,and then got to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.97,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,It looks like I'm the only \Nnew recruit this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:17.34,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,That's kinda lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:20.45,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:22.35,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,Don't be negative, Aoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:25.05,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,Get friendly with the girl next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:26.96,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:33.09,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,It didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.44,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,I think this is a good pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:52.53,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,What kind of company is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:53.16,sign_11330_125_Please_present_c,,0,0,0,,Please Hold Your Card \NUp To The Circle
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:53.49,sign_11345_126_Needs_Fill,,0,0,0,,Open
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:08:00.66,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,I wonder if the girl at \Nthat desk is absent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.16,Main,hifumi,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:04.46,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.66,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,H-Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:14.41,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm Suzukaze Aoba. I'm starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:16.51,Main,hifumi,0,0,0,,Takimoto Hifumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.80,Main,hifumi,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:20.27,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Are you also on the character team?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.52,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:26.86,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:29.25,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,I don't think I can make any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:36.34,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.16,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Why is there a cat here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:42.88,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,You're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.37,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,Hey, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:46.54,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,You came all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:50.05,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,Are you the new employee, Suzukaze Aoba-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.49,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,Pardon me for my cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:54.88,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Oh, no problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:05.06,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,You're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:10.77,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,I'm Hazuki Shizuku, the director \Nof the game this team is making.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:12.11,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:13.69,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:16.09,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,So who's the cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.66,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,He's Mozuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.07,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,I bring him in sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.33,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,If I leave him at home all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:23.20,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,he gets bored and messes up the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:26.08,Main,umiko,0,0,0,,Hazuki-san, I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.64,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,Oh, Umiko-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:29.92,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:32.89,Main,umiko,0,0,0,,You're very late for the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:35.23,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,Oh, oopsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:37.13,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,Let's not look so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.55,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,That's how you get wrinkles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.10,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.86,Main,umiko,0,0,0,,Let's go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:47.28,Main,umiko,0,0,0,,Everyone's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:51.81,Main,shizu,0,0,0,,Suzukaze-kun, good luck with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:53.11,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:57.82,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,Maybe the director's not very important...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:03.29,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,A private message?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:05.89,Italics,hifumi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.83,Italics,hifumi,0,0,0,,I'm not very good at speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:11.84,Italics,hifumi,0,0,0,,I'm also on the character team, so ask \Nme anything if you have any questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:14.37,Italics,hifumi,0,0,0,,Also, just call me Hifumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:15.88,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,Hifumi-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:19.65,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Hey, newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:21.55,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,C-Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:24.07,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Have you done any 3D?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:28.15,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I don't know anything besides drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:30.19,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Okay, that's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:34.70,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Then do chapter one of this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:35.94,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.77,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:40.52,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:42.21,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:45.67,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.63,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,I don't understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:49.99,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,But who do I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.71,sign_15617_187_From_Hifumi,on-screen,0,0,0,,From Hifumi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.71,sign_15617_188_I_m_sorry_about_,on-screen,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about earlier!\NI'm not very good at speaking.\NI'm also on the character team,\Nso ask me anything\Nif you have any questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:57.23,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Hifumi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:59.80,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Could I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:03.31,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:05.05,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Hifumi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:07.12,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.35,sign_16060_194_From_Ko_IWannaLe,on-screen,0,0,0,,From Ko@IWannaLeaveOnTime
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.35,sign_16060_195_Behind_you__Behi,on-screen,0,0,0,,Behind you! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.02,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:14.39,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:15.65,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.53,Main,ko,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:25.70,Main,hifumi,0,0,0,,Do you have a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:26.57,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:28.00,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:30.53,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,But I think I've already figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.21,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I got another private message.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:43.43,Italics,ko,0,0,0,,If you have questions for \NHifumin, send her a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.21,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Yagami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:47.18,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:49.25,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,Sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:52.83,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,My apologies for distracting you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:54.67,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,I had a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:12:00.04,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,It says you can hide all but the \Nselected object, in the book,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:02.28,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,but I can't find the toolbox for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.79,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,Where could I find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:05.35,Italics,hifumi,0,0,0,,You don't need to use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:08.78,Italics,hifumi,0,0,0,,Just use the Ctrl+H keyboard shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:10.64,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,That solved the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:11.57,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:13.16,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm very grateful for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:14.52,Italics,hifumi,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:17.33,Italics,hifumi,0,0,0,,But no need to be so formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:18.86,Italics,hifumi,0,0,0,,Smile! Smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.94,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,What? But I'm new here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:23.31,Italics,hifumi,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:26.71,Italics,hifumi,0,0,0,,Everyone here's pretty friendly, \Nso don't be so tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:28.60,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.33,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:31.65,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:32.53,Italics,hifumi,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:34.79,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:36.24,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:38.37,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,I think I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.99,Main,ko,0,0,0,,I got a message from Aoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:47.40,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm doing the assignments in the book!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.62,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,Easy peasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.70,Main,ko,0,0,0,,She got influenced so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:56.32,Italics,ko,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:58.52,Italics,ko,0,0,0,,Could you come see me at my desk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:01.84,Italics,ko,0,0,0,,I need to teach you a few things, \Nlike how to use private messaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:01.84,sign_18722_239_Uh______________,on-screen,0,0,0,,Uh                                      oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:05.95,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I-I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.30,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Just know your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:30.24,Italics,hajime,0,0,0,,Yun, don't you think you should take \NSuzukaze-san to lunch as her senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:35.94,Italics,yun,0,0,0,,I'm all for lunch, \Nbut why don't you invite her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:37.97,Italics,hajime,0,0,0,,You invite her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:40.65,Italics,yun,0,0,0,,You're such a coward. Aren't you her senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:51.16,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,Suzukaze-san, you want to go out for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:52.81,Main,yun,0,0,0,,I'll come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:56.39,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,U-Um, what about Hifumi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:05.12,Main,yun,0,0,0,,Hifumi-senpai doesn't \Nusually go out to lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:06.75,Main,yun,0,0,0,,You wanna come out today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:08.94,Main,hifumi,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:11.78,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for disturbing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:14.92,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I hope you'll join us next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:19.21,Main,hifumi,0,0,0,,Aoba-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:25.30,Main,hifumi,0,0,0,,I-I think I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.00,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Aoba, wanna go out for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.83,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:33.31,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Wh-What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.35,Main,yun,0,0,0,,I haven't introduced myself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:39.68,Main,yun,0,0,0,,I'm Ijima Yun on the character team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.31,Main,yun,0,0,0,,She and I joined the same year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:44.77,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,I'm Shinoda Hajime on the motion team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:45.98,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,Nice to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:48.57,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:50.97,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:52.88,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,It's my first time having a kouhai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.93,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,And we've only just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:58.68,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Please don't worry. You're my senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.66,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Shinoda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.80,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,"Senpai"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:05.69,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,That gives me goosebumps, \Nso just call me Hajime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.85,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Hajime-san, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.67,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,You can just call me Aoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:14.34,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Aoba... san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:16.47,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,Wait, is that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:22.69,Main,yun,0,0,0,,She was asking me to invite you \Nin private messaging earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:23.45,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:25.22,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,Don't tell her that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:25.98,Main,yun,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:28.57,Main,yun,0,0,0,,You're nervous because she's \Nyour first kouhai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.70,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,Isn't she your first kouhai, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:37.56,Main,yun,0,0,0,,You were worried about her when she was \Ntrying to talk to Hifumi-senpai earlier, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:40.20,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,Don't tell her that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:44.80,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.59,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,Everyone seems so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.27,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:53.93,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Let's get this done!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:01.20,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,But first, I need to use the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:13.03,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Bathroom, bathroom... \NWhen you gotta go, you gotta—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:18.12,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Y-Yagami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:20.72,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:24.08,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I went to use the restroom, \Nbut I didn't have my ID card,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.62,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,so I couldn't open the office door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:27.63,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.38,Main,ko,0,0,0,,The bathroom is outside the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:34.11,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Without your ID card, \Nyou can't get into the office,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:36.55,Main,ko,0,0,0,,but we also can't track your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:40.35,Main,ko,0,0,0,,What is the management thinking, \Nforgetting to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:46.05,Main,rin,0,0,0,,Ko-chan, did you already take \NAoba-chan's ID card picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:47.03,Main,ko,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.06,Main,rin,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:49.86,Main,rin,0,0,0,,I asked you to do it this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:58.41,Main,ko,0,0,0,,I'll do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.38,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Stand in front of the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:02.66,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:09.21,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,You know, you can wear \Nwhatever you want here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:10.87,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,but why are you in your school uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:12.14,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.44,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,This isn't a school uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:15.09,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,This is a suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.17,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm an adult, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.68,Italics,ko,0,0,0,,It looks like a uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:24.18,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Then at least learn how \Nto wear a suit properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:29.81,Italics,ko,0,0,0,,She doesn't look good in a suit \Nbecause she looks like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:31.24,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:34.03,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I heard what you were thinking just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:37.65,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Well, take two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:42.29,Main,ko,0,0,0,,I don't have enough light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:44.57,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Hajime, can I borrow your light?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:47.53,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,I don't have any light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:49.29,Main,ko,0,0,0,,You have that light sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.64,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Hey, perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:53.85,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:58.31,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Look forward to the finished product.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:00.10,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.75,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,You couldn't come back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.75,0:18:02.77,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:05.98,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I didn't know what to do, \Nand I was about to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:07.94,Main,yun,0,0,0,,You really had it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.23,Main,yun,0,0,0,,Want to relax with some snacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:16.70,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:20.15,Italics,aoba,0,0,0,,Hifumi-senpai, would you like some snacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:22.02,Italics,hifumi,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:23.93,Italics,hifumi,0,0,0,,I brought some cookies today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:25.61,Main,hifumi,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:28.21,Main,3,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:32.99,Main,yun,0,0,0,,Aoba-chan, you're learning 3D, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:33.93,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:36.72,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm trying to learn as fast as \Npossible, so I can help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:39.97,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,What's the release date of the \Ngame we're making right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:42.04,Main,yun,0,0,0,,When was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:43.10,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,It's in six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:47.96,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,The rumor is, we're going \Nto get super busy soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:48.76,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:49.85,Main,hifumi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:54.73,Main,hifumi,0,0,0,,You won't be able to go home for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:58.49,Italics,hajime,0,0,0,,It doesn't sound like a joke \Nwhen you speak like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:02.22,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,But Yagami-san was already sleeping here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:03.83,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Is it because she's the leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:07.98,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,I think it's accurate to say she lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:09.10,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,She's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.92,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,She does several times more \Nwork than everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:15.53,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,Though she has some personality problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:21.73,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Aoba, thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:23.18,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Here's your ID card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:27.18,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Now I really feel like an official employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:29.43,Main,ko,0,0,0,,You already were official.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:33.07,Main,ko,0,0,0,,It's fine to take breaks, \Nbut you guys are still clocked in,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.92,Main,ko,0,0,0,,so make sure you get back to work soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:35.94,Main,4,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:38.73,Main,ko,0,0,0,,So how far have you gotten, Aoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:40.09,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:41.71,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:43.49,Main,ko,0,0,0,,That's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:46.20,Main,ko,0,0,0,,I'll send you some work \Nsoon, then, so be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:49.28,Main,ko,0,0,0,,You'll learn the small \Nthings through experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:50.71,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:53.99,Main,rin,0,0,0,,How's Aoba-chan doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:56.59,Main,ko,0,0,0,,I'm glad she seems to be a fast learner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:58.60,Main,ko,0,0,0,,She might turn out to be reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:00.05,sign_28753_372_Artist_,on-screen,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,300)}Artist
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:03.64,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Let's work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:11.18,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,But first, I need to use the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:21.71,Main,ko,0,0,0,,B-B-B-Bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:25.31,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Yagami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.76,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:34.79,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,Yagami-san, you're not staying here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:39.23,Main,ko,0,0,0,,I wouldn't last if I stayed \Novernight every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:40.88,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Rin would get mad at me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:43.21,Main,yun,0,0,0,,Rin-san gets mad, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:45.17,Main,ko,0,0,0,,She gets mad a lot sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:47.89,sign_29836_383_Artist,on-screen,0,0,0,,Artist
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:46.69,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.77,Main,ko,0,0,0,,How was your first day?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:55.40,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Do you have any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:57.18,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:20:59.66,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:03.39,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I forgot to ask you something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:04.34,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:05.57,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:11.66,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,What's the title of the \Nnew video game we're making?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:15.54,Main,ko,0,0,0,,Oh, no one told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:18.53,Main,hajime,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:21.80,Main,yun,0,0,0,,We forgot to tell her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:27.53,Main,ko,0,0,0,,We're making the third installment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:29.68,Main,ko,0,0,0,,of {\i1}Fairies Story{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:43.75,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,That's the video game that made me \Nwant to be a character designer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.73,0:21:46.59,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:48.55,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Thank you for having me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.54,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.08,0:22:07.12,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fairies Story 3{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.79,0:22:16.31,sign_32003_403_Nenecchi,on-screen,0,0,0,,Nenecchi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:19.31,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,It's Nenecchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.31,0:22:20.89,Italics,nene,0,0,0,,Aocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.89,0:22:21.77,Italics,nene,0,0,0,,Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:24.57,Italics,nene,0,0,0,,{\i0}Moon Ranger{\i1}'s getting a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.93,0:22:26.76,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:27.90,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I've never heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:30.03,Italics,nene,0,0,0,,It's a popular anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:33.47,Italics,nene,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I've supported it for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.47,0:22:35.80,Italics,nene,0,0,0,,Let's go together when it premiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:37.70,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:40.78,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm tired today, so I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:41.67,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:43.85,Italics,nene,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:46.30,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:50.77,Italics,nene,0,0,0,,Well, I figured you had a \Nrough first day at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.77,0:22:54.94,Italics,nene,0,0,0,,So I didn't want to make you \Ntalk about work at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:22:59.06,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,It wasn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:00.78,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,Get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.78,0:23:03.07,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,It was incredible at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:05.51,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,You know Yagami Ko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.51,0:23:08.34,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,She did the character \Ndesign for {\i1}Fairies Story{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:10.55,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm going to be working with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:11.29,Italics,nene,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:12.89,Italics,nene,0,0,0,,That's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:15.56,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm gonna work really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.21,0:23:19.42,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I'm gonna work really hard \Nand learn how to do my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:23.81,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,In order to make a new game.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:28.83,Main,nene,0,0,0,,Aocchi, is a video game company really busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.83,0:23:30.17,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,I don't know, Nenecchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.17,0:23:32.04,Main,aoba,0,0,0,,But there was someone who slept at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:34.93,Main,nene,0,0,0,,Did you run into someone \Nsleeping in her underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:37.01,Main,nene,0,0,0,,Just kidding. No adult does that.
